<br>
In the past Verant has recommended new servers to be RP heavy (Brell Serilis for example).  However, without that tag on the server selection screen, people new to EQ, or those old players that did not pay attention to EQ news, had no way of knowing that RPing was strongly encouraged for Brell.  In the beginning the server was a fabulous RP environment, and still is compared to most others, but with time RPing slowly eroded as more and more powergamers joined in.<br>
<br>
Will some powergamers still drift to a RP-tagged server?  Sure.  But give 10 pgamers and 10 RPers a choice between new RP and non-RP servers and I can guarantee most would go their separate ways.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
